			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Oh yeah - and before I forget again - consider.
<br />

<br />
Rangers got jolt because rangers would simply die again and again and again.  Rangers needed fixing
<br />

<br />
Rogues got evade because without it they couldnt do their damage, and given how useful all the other rogue skills weren't, they needed it.
<br />

<br />

<br />
BL dont need to be behind a mob, nor do they die horribly just for getting agro.  Basically - BL don't need it.
<br />

<br />

<br />
I am not sure what level you are at - and I agree there are times throughout a BL's career when the mobs are hitting harder than you would like, but really - BL can survive and do good damage and utility even without Jolt/FD/DA.
<br />

<br />
Learn how to manage agro.  If things seem rough now for you - dont worry, things get better.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
